Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.38,0:00:15.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Blood pressure, 120/80.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.59,0:00:17.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Pulse, 92.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.84,0:00:19.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to begin extracting the bullets.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.77,0:00:31.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Bullet extracted.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.86,0:00:36.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Extraction complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.65,0:00:40.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's still too early to relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.24,0:00:43.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We still have to reinforce the damaged blood vessel walls.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.12,0:00:45.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.16,0:00:47.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Proline sutures!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.37,0:00:48.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.37,0:02:24.20,Stuff,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(357,306)}Downfall
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.73,0:02:31.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Blood pressure, 128/72.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.46,0:02:33.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Pulse, 88.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.82,0:02:35.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like there are still some residual effects from the anesthesia
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.12,0:02:47.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do your best...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.08,0:02:49.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do your best, and live...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.98,0:02:55.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Boyer!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.72,0:02:59.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it went smoothly on your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.63,0:03:01.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, the operation was successful, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.18,0:03:04.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The mayor passed away.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.43,0:03:09.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.52,0:03:11.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's... too bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.86,0:03:15.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised you can talk as if \N it has nothing with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.61,0:03:21.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You left our team just before the operation, didn't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.28,0:03:24.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But that boy was brought in before the mayor, so I...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.53,0:03:26.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell cares who came in first?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.04,0:03:31.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The problem is that you created a \N hole in the team you left...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.25,0:03:32.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...so we were forced to fill that gap!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.67,0:03:35.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please listen to me!  I was...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.46,0:03:37.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You destroyed the balance of our teamwork.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.88,0:03:45.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I followed the director's orders and instructed \N you to operate on the mayor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.22,0:03:45.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,However, you ignored that order!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.81,0:03:48.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,However, you ignored that order!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.31,0:03:50.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, chief!  At the time...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.52,0:03:55.44,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Surgery is something that depends \N on the staff trusting each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.90,0:03:58.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And yet, you acted on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.15,0:04:01.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've already informed the director about this, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.49,0:04:08.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The director deeply regrets the damage to the \N hospital's reputation this case will cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.75,0:04:10.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better be prepared!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.17,0:04:15.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,E-Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.50,0:04:17.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.51,0:04:22.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.80,0:04:28.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The boy's current blood pressure is 114/82, pulse 84.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.81,0:04:31.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,His vital signs are all perfectly stable.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.27,0:04:33.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.85,0:04:35.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's good to hear...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.65,0:04:39.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm... I thought the operation \N you just performed was great!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.26,0:04:50.68,Stuff,,0000,0000,0000,,After collapsing at his retreat...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.68,0:04:53.19,Stuff,,0000,0000,0000,,...Mr. Roedecker passed away at the \N hospital where was being treated.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.39,0:04:56.77,Stuff,,0000,0000,0000,,After hearing of his death...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.77,0:04:59.44,Stuff,,0000,0000,0000,,...many residents flocked to City Hall with flowers and such...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.44,0:05:01.69,Stuff,,0000,0000,0000,,...and mourned the passing of the mayor.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.53,0:05:06.16,Stuff,,0000,0000,0000,,A press conference was recently held at Eisler Memorial Hospital...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.16,0:05:07.70,Stuff,,0000,0000,0000,,...where the mayor was treated.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.85,0:05:11.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayor Roedecker's cause of death...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.39,0:05:15.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...was a cerebral infarction caused by the \N occlusion of the internal carotid artery.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.73,0:05:18.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We gave it our best...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.48,0:05:20.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...but due to advanced brain swelling...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.82,0:05:23.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...it ended with a very unfortunate result.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.22,0:05:28.18,Stuff,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, regarding the details about the \N Mayor's successor in this situation...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.18,0:05:31.68,Stuff,,0000,0000,0000,,...City Hall commented that they will work them out immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.18,0:05:36.69,Stuff,,0000,0000,0000,,Regarding the murder of Mr. Liebert and his \N wife at the edge of town late last night...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.52,0:05:40.02,Stuff,,0000,0000,0000,,...due to evidence found during a search of the house...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.02,0:05:41.19,Stuff,,0000,0000,0000,,...it was either a possible robbery...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.82,0:05:46.95,Stuff,,0000,0000,0000,,...or a politically-motivated terrorist attack \N against the now deceased couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.95,0:05:49.16,Stuff,,0000,0000,0000,,An investigation is underway into both scenarios.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.28,0:05:31.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to get to sleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.64,0:05:52.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,With regard to one of the couple's twins...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.70,0:05:54.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The elder brother was shot in the head.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.62,0:05:58.96,Stuff,,0000,0000,0000,,Although his operation was a success, he has not yet regained consciousness...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.96,0:06:00.29,Stuff,,0000,0000,0000,,...and is still in critical condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.34,0:06:03.42,Stuff,,0000,0000,0000,,Next is the weather.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.34,0:06:07.55,Stuff,,0000,0000,0000,,There should be clear weather across the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.55,0:06:10.55,Stuff,,0000,0000,0000,,However, it will begin to rain during the afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.57,0:06:08.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what that child's going to do now...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.57,0:06:12.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the same as that child...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.91,0:06:19.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Reinhart in ICU keeps saying hat he can't get to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.63,0:06:22.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't we prescribe him some sleeping pills or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.34,0:06:29.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you listening to me, Dr. Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.05,0:06:30.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.55,0:06:36.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, please give him a dose of Halcion.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.56,0:06:43.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, he's been spaced out the entire day!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.03,0:06:48.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Becker?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.53,0:06:51.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you are in a lot of trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.34,0:06:53.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Has the director punished you yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.12,0:07:01.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I keep tell you that \N a hospital is a world of politics.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.17,0:07:04.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If only you had obediently listened to him...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.25,0:07:07.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...you would have had smooth sailing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.30,0:07:13.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess this means you'll be like me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.27,0:07:20.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't look so glum.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.56,0:07:23.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There'll be chances for you to regain your reputation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.73,0:07:26.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just go out and blow this whole thing off!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.49,0:07:33.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.28,0:07:33.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.03,0:07:38.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Would I be able to question the twin girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.18,0:07:40.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't time for that, detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.58,0:07:43.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's disappeared from her room!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.00,0:07:45.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.00,0:07:51.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She likes to sneak away from her room \N and wander around the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.06,0:08:02.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill... him...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.00,0:08:07.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill... him...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.97,0:08:15.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill... him...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.49,0:08:19.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And so...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.95,0:08:26.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...the reason Eisler Memorial Hospital has secured its \N place as the leader of our nation's medical society...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.54,0:08:32.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...is without a doubt because it is blessed \N by talented people such as yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.38,0:08:34.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I thank you from the bottom of my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.76,0:08:42.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was very unfortunate that the mayor passed \N away at our hospital the other day...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.52,0:08:45.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...but we gave it everything we had, just as we always do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.31,0:08:50.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The way the public views our hospital \N has not changed at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.36,0:08:58.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's give a round of applause to Dr. Boyer and Dr. Eisen, \N who gave everything they had to save the mayor's life!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.80,0:09:18.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I took a look at your thesis.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.39,0:09:20.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please keep up the good work!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.31,0:09:29.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Director.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.77,0:09:35.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I must apologize for what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.61,0:09:40.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now.  That's already in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.87,0:09:42.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Director?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.24,0:09:45.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You did what you thought was best.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.29,0:09:46.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that good enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.17,0:09:48.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Director...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.58,0:09:49.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Director...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.79,0:09:55.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Next, we'd like to have the chief \N neurosurgeon give a few words.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.05,0:09:58.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please excuse me, I've just been called.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.89,0:10:01.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not calling for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.72,0:10:06.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please welcome our newly inaugurated chief, Dr. Boyer!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.89,0:10:08.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please give us a few words!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.35,0:10:09.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, come this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.86,0:10:13.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Director!  What is this...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.69,0:10:16.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you wish to stay at the hospital, then stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.07,0:10:20.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But it'd be best to give up your dream \N of rising to the top as a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.12,0:10:23.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible for someone with \N an attitude problem, like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.12,0:10:27.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I admire your skills, but that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.79,0:10:31.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget about presenting at academy meetings as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.63,0:10:36.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But, director!  Please hear me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.63,0:10:38.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you want to transfer to another hospital...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.68,0:10:40.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...I have no intention of writing a letter \N of recommendation for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.68,0:10:44.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It means that it's pointless to \N have any ambitions anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.37,0:10:48.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The path of being the doctor you \N dreamed of is closed to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.28,0:11:02.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,At the heart of an operation, lies teamwork.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.22,0:11:05.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Only when each of our skills come together...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.29,0:11:06.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...can we save lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.47,0:11:20.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eva...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.68,0:11:27.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eva, can't you say something to your father about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.64,0:11:29.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't do anything wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.68,0:11:33.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I only performed the operation in the order the patients were brought in!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.83,0:11:48.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's... the engagement ring I gave you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.62,0:11:51.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You really are a fool
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.88,0:12:00.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eva!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.30,0:12:03.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that suit looks spectacular, Dr. Norden!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.93,0:12:07.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You look rather dazzling tonight yourself, Eva.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.46,0:12:41.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think it's a funny story?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.31,0:12:46.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I came across Director Heinemann's thesis...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.13,0:12:47.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...came over to Germany...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.63,0:12:49.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...and worked under him, until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.88,0:12:52.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Although now that I think about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.22,0:12:54.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...the thesis that made such a deep impression on me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.51,0:13:00.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...was probably written for the director \N by someone else, just like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.52,0:13:04.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew I was being used....
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.65,0:13:08.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...But I believed that if I rose to a sufficient status...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.23,0:13:11.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'd be able to conduct as much \N of my own research as I wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.82,0:13:17.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even before saving lives, we doctors value academics first.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.16,0:13:17.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.29,0:13:19.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.62,0:13:21.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A doctor's first priority is saving lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.21,0:13:25.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,People's lives aren't equal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.71,0:13:26.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.71,0:13:28.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No life is worth more or less than any other!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.17,0:13:31.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I am not wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.22,0:13:33.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I have an attitude problem, you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.43,0:13:34.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you, then?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.70,0:13:36.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not a doctor!  You are just in it for the money!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.49,0:13:40.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,People like him...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.54,0:13:42.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...are better off dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.99,0:13:52.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I should thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.70,0:13:57.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You opened my eyes as a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.03,0:13:59.28,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep on living.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.99,0:14:02.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I lost everything to perform your operation, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.50,0:14:09.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I took extreme measures to bring you back to life.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.42,0:14:38.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You should at least know your name, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.43,0:14:41.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Your name is Anna Liebert, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.52,0:14:52.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I said, detective.  \N It's still impossible right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.11,0:14:54.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you do something about her, doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.28,0:14:59.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, her parents were shot and \N killed right before her eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.32,0:15:01.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though she doesn't have any external injuries...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.37,0:15:04.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...it seems as though she's suffering from a case of amnesia, induced by intense fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.29,0:15:09.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Can we ask you to postpone your question for a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.42,0:15:12.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard to handle these types of cases!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.29,0:15:15.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The victim was an East German trade adviser.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.21,0:15:19.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't solve this quickly, the federal police are going to take over.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.72,0:15:24.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Those bastards always come in afterwards, and take all the credit from the local police!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.47,0:15:26.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have time to take it easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.81,0:15:28.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, how about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.94,0:15:30.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see her see her brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.98,0:15:33.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe she'll feel relieved, and \N her memory will come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.78,0:15:38.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm offended by such a risky plan that \N only an amateur would come up with!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.82,0:15:41.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, I doubt Dr. Tenma would authorize it anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.82,0:15:42.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.99,0:15:44.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The attending physician for her older brother, Johan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.54,0:15:49.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what the hell am I supposed to do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.32,0:15:57.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo, Dr. Tenma!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.40,0:15:59.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you look so out of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.03,0:16:00.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You look pretty tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.66,0:16:04.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been pretty busy lately with \N emergency operations, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.78,0:16:08.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They sure are abusing you, just because you \N were demoted from being the chief...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.62,0:16:11.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.35,0:16:13.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, I feel better.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.13,0:16:15.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey.  You sure you are okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.59,0:16:19.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.82,0:16:21.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They are calling me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.09,0:16:25.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still working even though you're so tired?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.12,0:16:28.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't get anywhere by exhausting yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.44,0:16:31.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at this, director.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.56,0:16:35.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at all these presents and letters of encouragement.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.84,0:16:38.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a mountain of them in his sister's room as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.44,0:16:41.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is what we get...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.07,0:16:45.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...because the media gave such a tear jerking \N account of how their parents were killed...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.83,0:16:46.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...and now all they have is each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.70,0:16:53.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But to the hospital, he's just a troublesome \N patient who can't pay the treatment costs.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.21,0:16:57.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now.  What's wrong with tear jerking?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.00,0:17:01.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This means that people will be paying more attention to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.22,0:17:05.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That alone makes these kids worthwhile.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.26,0:17:05.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.72,0:17:07.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.60,0:17:10.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, how about that something like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.64,0:17:16.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's present the media with a photo \N of the two sibling being reunited.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.31,0:17:20.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, the media has requested that numerous times.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.82,0:17:22.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do it, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.11,0:17:28.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A photo of the two siblings alive and well, reuniting under the warm care of our hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.49,0:17:34.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But the attending physician says that it's \N still too early for the two to meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.75,0:17:36.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's the attending physician?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.92,0:17:38.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.88,0:17:40.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then remove him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.46,0:17:41.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.55,0:17:46.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That man doesn't need to be in the spotlight here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.80,0:17:49.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Remove Dr. Tenma as attending physician.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.72,0:17:50.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.56,0:17:57.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a friendly present from the kind citizens.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.02,0:17:58.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you guys like some?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.69,0:18:00.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,T-Thank you, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.12,0:18:10.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you feel, Mrs. Hankel?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.58,0:18:13.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.62,0:18:16.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel wonderful, thanks to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.33,0:18:18.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be able to take the stitches out soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.54,0:18:20.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's not long now before you can leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.13,0:18:22.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That means I can go home?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.76,0:18:26.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,However, please follow my instructions \N and get plenty of rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.88,0:18:28.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.26,0:18:33.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please prescribe daily anticonvolusive and \N hypotensive drugs to Mrs. Hankel, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.23,0:18:40.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Pull yourself together!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.65,0:18:44.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What are you guys doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.44,0:18:44.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Tenma!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.99,0:18:48.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We let her see her brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.16,0:18:50.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She suddenly started screaming \N at the top of her lungs, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.95,0:18:52.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you let them see each other?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.38,0:19:03.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.71,0:19:04.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and take her back to her room!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.92,0:19:05.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, sir.!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.55,0:19:08.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the meaning of this, Dr. Boyer?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.80,0:19:10.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that camera?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.09,0:19:16.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, we're going to reveal the heart warming \N reunion of the two siblings to the media.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.77,0:19:20.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Under whose authorization are you doing this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.27,0:19:23.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Johan is no longer under your care.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.67,0:19:27.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Starting today, I'll be in charge of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.90,0:19:30.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And I decided it was okay for the two to meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.29,0:19:35.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you dare...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.79,0:19:38.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you dare turn these two \Ninto some kind of exhibition!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.87,0:19:40.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is an order from the director.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.42,0:19:43.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it'd be in your best interest \N if you didn't disobey him anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.54,0:19:45.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I saved his life!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.30,0:19:47.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my responsibility to care for \N him until he fully recovers!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.05,0:19:50.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you think so, why don't you just \N look at the boy's response?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.31,0:19:59.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The second he saw his little sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.98,0:20:02.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...he stretched out his arm and began to cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.77,0:20:06.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's regained his senses, and is \N displaying normal responses.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.82,0:20:09.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This means your operation was a great success.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.53,0:20:10.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.49,0:20:13.24,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Your work here is done.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.74,0:20:16.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now hurry up and get back to your station.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.92,0:20:31.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The hell with all of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.84,0:20:35.91,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Director's orders, my ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.91,0:20:38.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief's orders my ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.43,0:20:43.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All they care about are money and their stupid positions!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.77,0:20:46.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.20,0:20:59.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.47,0:21:14.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home, father!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.18,0:21:19.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Father?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.35,0:21:20.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you in your room?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.57,0:21:32.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Chief?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.95,0:21:34.74,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're holding a meeting this late?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.76,0:21:55.13,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you asleep already, father?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.18,0:21:59.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.37,0:22:25.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They're better off dead...
